OL,3,CVictims of fugitive paedophile finally
OL,4,Cface him after 30 years on the run
OL,6,FVictims of a paedophile former scout
OL,7,Fleader who went on the run for almost
OL,8,F30 years have finally faced him in
OL,9,Fcourt as a sentencing judge told them
OL,10,Fonly one person was at fault for the
OL,11,Fabuse they suffered.
OL,13,FRichard Burrows, 81, systematically
OL,14,Fabused 24 young boys, some as young as
OL,15,Fnine or 10, across Cheshire and the
OL,16,FMidlands between 1968 and 1995.
