OL,3,CVictims of fugitive paedophile finally
OL,4,Cface him after 30 years on the run
OL,6,FBut after he was charged with the
OL,7,Fallegations of child sexual abuse in
OL,8,F1997 he fled to Thailand for 27 years
OL,9,Fusing a stolen identity - Peter Smith
OL,10,F- to evade detection.
OL,12,FHe was finally arrested in March 2024
OL,13,Fafter he flew to Heathrow airport when
OL,14,Fhe ran out of money. Officers were
OL,15,Fwaiting for him after using facial
OL,16,Frecognition technology on his custody
OL,17,Fphoto - which led to a match in
OL,18,FThailand.
