OL,3,CVictims of fugitive paedophile finally
OL,4,Cface him after 30 years on the run
OL,6,FHe was then charged with further
OL,7,Foffences which had been reported after
OL,8,Fhe disappeared.
OL,10,FBurrows was found guilty by a jury at
OL,11,FChester Crown Court in March of 54
OL,12,Foffences including indecent assault of
OL,13,Fboys, buggery, attempted buggery and
OL,14,Findecency with a child.
