OL,3,CVictims of fugitive paedophile finally
OL,4,Cface him after 30 years on the run
OL,6,FHis offending in Cheshire took place
OL,7,Fbetween 1969 and 1971 while he was
OL,8,Femployed as a housemaster looking
OL,9,Fafter vulnerable children at Danesford
OL,10,FChildren's Home in Congleton.
OL,12,FHis victims in the Midlands were
OL,13,Fabused between 1968 and 1995, the
OL,14,Fmajority through local Scout groups
OL,15,Fwhere Burrows worked as a leader.
OL,17,FIn each case he befriended the boys
OL,18,Fusing his position of trust.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/13
