OL,3,CVictims of fugitive paedophile finally
OL,4,Cface him after 30 years on the run
OL,6,FA number of his victims faced the
OL,7,Fperpetrator as he watched on from the
OL,8,Fdock wearing headphones, as his
OL,9,Fsentencing hearing began at Chester
OL,10,FCrown Court. Other victims' statements
OL,11,Fwere read out to the court.
OL,13,FOne told the court that Burrows had
OL,14,F"stripped away my humanity" after he
OL,15,Fwas taken away to the defendant's tent
OL,16,Fon his first camping trip with the
OL,17,FScouts and subjected to an eight-hour
OL,18,Fordeal.
