OL,3,CVictims of fugitive paedophile finally
OL,4,Cface him after 30 years on the run
OL,6,FHe said he twice attempted to take his
OL,7,Fown life and felt "perpetual trauma,
OL,8,Fshame and despair".
OL,10,FThe Honorary Recorder of Chester,
OL,11,FJudge Steven Everett, told him: "You
OL,12,Fhave done nothing to be ashamed of."
OL,14,FAnother victim said at the time he hid
OL,15,Fthe abuse from his parents, could not
OL,16,Ftell any of his friends or trust a
OL,17,Fgrown-up any more.
