OL,3,CVictims of fugitive paedophile finally
OL,4,Cface him after 30 years on the run
OL,6,FHe said: "I had no-one to turn to and
OL,7,Fjust internalised it all. It totally
OL,8,Faffected my future relationships and
OL,9,Fbehaviour.
OL,11,F"Even now I keep going through my
OL,12,Fhead: 'Why did you assault me? I
OL,13,Flooked up to you.'"
OL,15,FJudge Everett told him: "I want to be
OL,16,Fcrystal clear. There is only one
OL,17,Fperson at fault here and he is sitting
OL,18,Fopposite me in the dock.
