OL,3,CVictims of fugitive paedophile finally
OL,4,Cface him after 30 years on the run
OL,6,F"I suspect every single person in the
OL,7,Fcourtroom, bar one, feels totally
OL,8,Fsorry for you."
OL,10,FThe court heard Burrows was dismissed
OL,11,Ffrom Danesford Children's Home after
OL,12,Fone of his victims, who has since
OL,13,Fdied, complained at the time that he
OL,14,Fhad been indecently assaulted.
OL,16,FHe later told police in 1995 that he
OL,17,Fthought he was not believed at the
OL,18,Ftime and added: "I believe deep inside
OL,19,FMr Burrows should be prosecuted and it
OL,20,Fshould have happened a long time ago."
