OL,3,CVictims of fugitive paedophile finally
OL,4,Cface him after 30 years on the run
OL,6,FAt trial, Burrows denied all the
OL,7,Foffences at Danesford as he claimed
OL,8,Fhis change in career path was an
OL,9,Feffort to do good rather than seek out
OL,10,Fmore victims.
OL,12,FPhil Clemo, defending, said: "Putting
OL,13,Fit bluntly, whatever sentence your
OL,14,Fhonour passes, he is going to die in
OL,15,Fprison.
OL,17,F"He spent 27 years in Thailand in a
OL,18,Fpleasant setting. The reality is his
OL,19,Flast days will be on the prison estate
OL,20,Fsomewhere.
OL,26,@tD@^OUyD@AOU
