OL,3,CVictims of fugitive paedophile finally
OL,4,Cface him after 30 years on the run
OL,6,F"He, of course, respects the verdicts
OL,7,Fof the jury even though he does not
OL,8,Fagree with it. He does accept on the
OL,9,Fmatters he has always accepted and
OL,10,Fknows he has caused incredible
OL,11,Fsuffering."
OL,13,FJudge Everett replied: "I didn't see
OL,14,Fmuch of that during the trial.
OL,16,F"He used the truly obnoxious saying
OL,17,F'good and bad paedophiles'. I have a
OL,18,Ffeeling that the jury was repulsed by
OL,19,Fthat.
