OL,6,F"His view was that a good paedophile
OL,7,Fdid things which did not harm and a
OL,8,Fbad one does cause harm.
OL,10,F"That thought process is so warped it
OL,11,Fis difficult to understand."
OL,13,FMr Clemo continued: "There were
OL,14,Fmoments when there were tears, not
OL,15,Fbefore the jury..."
OL,17,FThe judge said: "There were tears in
OL,18,Ffront of the jury but they were only
OL,19,Ftears for himself. As a person he
OL,20,Fdeserves no sympathy whatsoever."
